import React from 'react'
import styles from './MealItemForm.module.css'

const MealItemForm = (props) => {
    return (
        <>
            <form action="" className={styles.form}>
                <input type="text" />
                <button>
                    Add
                </button>
            </form>

        </>
    )
}

export default MealItemForm
